overview: Kathy Griffin renders a stand-up set at the Terrace Theater in Long Beach, Cal. Victims of Griffin's celeb-bashing wit include Miley Cyrus, Bristol Palin, Anderson Cooper, Oprah Winfrey and the Orange County housewives. Also: antics at the Grammy Awards; an encounter with Cher; and a letter from prison.
title: Kathy Griffin: Seaman 1st Class
